§431:10D-302  General life insurance provisions applicable.  The following [sections] of part I of this article shall apply to industrial life insurance policies:
     (1)  431:10D-104;
     (2)  431:10D-108;
     (3)  431:10D-109;
     (4)  431:10D-110; and
     (5)  431:10D-116. [L 1987, c 347, pt of §2]
